{"article_id":"Ns9vOocmcP8sP38x","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"They were a married couple","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"who left their baby with grandma","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"while they carried out the deadliest mass shooting in the United States since the December 2012 rampage at Sandy Hook .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Syed Rizwan Farook , a U.S. citizen , and his wife , Tashfeen Malik , a permanent resident , massacred 14 people at a holiday party Wednesday at the Inland Regional Center in San Bernardino , California .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Farook and Malik were later killed in a shootout with police .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The attackers ' specific motives remain unclear ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"but here is what we know about them :","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"He got to know Malik through an online dating service ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Farook family attorney Mohammad Abuershaid said .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"They met face to face","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"when Farook visited Saudi Arabia ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"where Malik had moved from her native Pakistan around the age of 18 or 20 ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"according to the lawyer .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"She later came to the United States on a fiancée visa","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and became a legal permanent resident .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"This image of Syed Rizwan Farook appears on the dating site iMilap.com .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"The couple left their 6-month-old girl with Farook 's mother Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"they had a doctor 's appointment .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The grandmother became concerned","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"when she saw reports of the shooting","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and could n't reach Farook .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Farook , an American citizen , was an environmental health specialist with the San Bernardino County health department ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"which was hosting the holiday party at the Inland Regional Center","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"where the attack took place .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"He had been there five years .","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Records list a man with his name and title","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"who worked at the agency","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and made $ 53,000 in 2013 .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"He graduated from California State University , San Bernardino , with a degree in environmental health in 2010 .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"A graduate student ID card from California State University , Fullerton , with Farook 's name on it was spotted by CNN on Friday inside his Redlands townhouse .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Jeff Cook , a spokesman for that school , said","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that records indicate","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"a student by that same name had been enrolled in Cal State Fullerton 's environmental engineering graduate program .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"The university issued a statement Friday","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"`` Syed Rizwan Farook attended Cal State Fullerton for one semester in Fall 2014 in the online graduate program in environmental engineering .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"He is not currently enrolled . ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Farook was at the party","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"but left abruptly before the shooting .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"He seemed angry ,","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"witnesses told police .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"He returned .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"And , along with Malik , he went into the building","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and began firing ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"authorities said .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":3},{"id":48,"text":"Shooting suspect 's brother-in-law :","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"' I am in shock '","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":3},{"id":51,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Shooting suspect 's brother-in-law :","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"' I am in shock '","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"01:11","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"There are no indications","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"his job was in jeopardy ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"police said .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"They 're also unaware of any criminal history .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Farhan Khan , Farook 's brother-in-law , told reporters","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"he was at a loss , too .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"`` I have no idea","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"why he would do something like this .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"I have absolutely no idea .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"I am in shock myself , ''","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Khan said .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"the family , like the rest of America , will have to wait for the police investigation for answers .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Farook and Malik did n't appear to have left behind a note ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"a law enforcement official said .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Law enforcement officials told CNN","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"that Farook had been in touch via phone and social media with at least one person","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"whom the FBI suspected of international terrorism .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"Officials would n't elaborate .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"It appears Farook was radicalized ,","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"which contributed to his motive ,","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"though other things","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"-- such as workplace grievances --","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"may have also played a role ,","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"other law enforcement sources said .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"The officials said","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"these contacts were not considered high-priority terrorism subjects .","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"And it had been at least a few months since the last known communication ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"they said .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Neither Farook nor Malik were on any list of potentially radicalized people ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"and there are no clear ties to overseas terrorist groups as of now ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"officials said .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Farook 's relatives knew him as conservative","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"but did n't think","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"he or his wife were extreme ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"according to the family 's attorneys .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"As the attack was underway ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"investigators believe","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"Malik expressed allegiance to ISIS leader Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi in a Facebook post ,","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"three U.S. officials familiar with the investigation told CNN .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"Malik made the post on an account with a different name ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"one U.S. official said .","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"The officials did not explain","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"how they knew","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"Malik was behind the message .","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"A law enforcement official said","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"it appeared ISIS may have inspired the attack ,","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"but none of the officials said","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"the terror group directed or ordered the attack .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"`` This is looking more and more like self-radicalization , ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"one law enforcement official said .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"`` He 's a little bit shy , a little bit withdrawn .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"He does n't mix with people easily , ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"said Mustafa Kuko , director of the Islamic Center of Riverside","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"where Farook was a regular .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Doyle Miller , Farook 's landlord , said","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"he had `` no cause for concern ''","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"when he rented out a townhouse to him in Redlands .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"`` He had no red flags whatsoever ;","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"everything checked out , ''","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"Miller said .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"`` He had good credit reports ... everything . `` We screen our people pretty good .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"It 's unbelievable what 's going on . ''","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Farook 's family knew him as someone","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"who `` always kept to himself , ''","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"as did his wife ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"according to Abuershaid .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Farook had a profile set up on iMilap.com ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"which describes itself as `` a site for people with disabilities and second marriage . ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"The profile said","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"he `` enjoys working on vintage and modern cars ,","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"reads religious books ,","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"enjoys eating out sometimes . ''","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"It also said","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"Farook `` enjoys traveling","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"and just hanging out in the backyard","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"doing target practice with his younger sister and friends . ''","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"He would go to firing ranges by himself ,","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"said David S. Chesley , another lawyer for Farook 's family .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"A representative for iMilap told CNN","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Farook logged on just twice in 2010","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and was n't active after that .","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"He did n't contact anyone ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"nor did anyone contact him ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"the site said .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"His father told the New York Daily News","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that Farook was religious .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"`` He would go to work ,","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"come back ,","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"go to pray ,","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"come back , ''","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"he said","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"Kuko , the Islamic Center director , said","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Farook would come to the center for morning and night prayers .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"He shares the same name as his brother and father","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"It 's important to note Farook 's middle name -- Rizwan .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"His father also is named Syed Farook ,","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"as is his older brother .","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"Like him , they have different middle names .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"The couple was `` dressed in dark , kind of tactical gear , ''","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"San Bernardino police Chief Jarrod Burguan said .","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"They carried rifles and semiautomatic handguns .","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"Two handguns","depth":19},{"id":158,"text":"recovered","depth":19},{"id":159,"text":"have been traced to Farook .","depth":18},{"id":160,"text":"He purchased them legally three or four years ago ,","depth":18},{"id":161,"text":"an official said .","depth":18},{"id":162,"text":"Two rifles were purchased by someone else , possibly a former roommate , also legally three or four years ago .","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"Officials said","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"they do n't think","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"that person had anything","depth":17},{"id":166,"text":"to do with the shooting .","depth":17},{"id":167,"text":"`` These were people","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"that came prepared , ''","depth":15},{"id":169,"text":"Burguan said .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"`` There had to have been some degree of planning","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"that went into this . ''","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"Two relatively new cellphones were found smashed","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"and tossed in a garbage can near one of the crime scenes ,","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"law enforcement officials said .","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"Officials suspect","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"the phones were damaged","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"to hide call histories .","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"A computer","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"found at the couple 's home","depth":15},{"id":180,"text":"was missing a hard drive .","depth":14},{"id":181,"text":"Investigators have subpoenaed email service providers","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"to retrieve communications .","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"Inside the garage of the couple 's rented townhouse , authorities found 12 pipe bomb-type devices and hundreds of tools ,","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"many of which could be used","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"to make improvised explosives .","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"A bag","depth":16},{"id":187,"text":"believed to belong to the shooters","depth":16},{"id":188,"text":"was found inside Inland Regional 's conference room .","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"Inside , investigators found three rudimentary explosive devices","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"packed with black powder","depth":17},{"id":191,"text":"and rigged to a remote-controlled toy car .","depth":17},{"id":192,"text":"The remote for the car was found inside the SUV","depth":18},{"id":193,"text":"where Farook and Malik were later killed ,","depth":18},{"id":194,"text":"a law enforcement official said .","depth":17},{"id":195,"text":"The pair planned to use the remote","depth":20},{"id":196,"text":"to detonate the explosives from a distance ,","depth":20},{"id":197,"text":"the official said .","depth":19},{"id":198,"text":"Either it did n't work","depth":20},{"id":199,"text":"because of distance","depth":20},{"id":200,"text":"or they did n't do it .","depth":19},{"id":201,"text":"Officials later rendered the explosive devices safe .","depth":17},{"id":202,"text":"After carrying out the attack at Inland Regional ,","depth":16},{"id":203,"text":"Farook and Malik led police on a chase .","depth":16},{"id":204,"text":"Farook fired at officers","depth":17},{"id":205,"text":"while Malik drove ,","depth":17},{"id":206,"text":"officials said .","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"They died in the shootout ,","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"which involved 21 officers .","depth":15}],"relations":[{"parent":417,"left":255,"right":416,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":231,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":214,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":0,"right":213,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":213,"left":211,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":210,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":215,"right":229,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":215,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":229,"left":223,"right":228,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":222,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":216,"right":221,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":219,"right":220,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":219,"left":218,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":10,"right":217,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS